---
title: Spinach and Cheese-Topped Pork Tenderloin with Oven Potatoes and Buttered Beans
description: Tonight we're trying something new! We are turning this pork tenderloin into medallions so we can top them with a luscious cheesy spinach dip. Oven-roasted potatoes and buttered green beans make a meal the whole family can get behind!
